    ▼
┌──────────────────────────┐
│   mcp-billing-gateway    │
│                          │
│  1. Authenticate caller  │
│  2. Check credits/sub    │
│  3. Debit payment        │
│  4. Forward JSON-RPC     │
│  5. Record usage         │
│  6. Return response      │
└──────────┬───────────────┘
           │
           ▼
┌──────────────────────────┐
│  Your MCP Server         │
│  (unchanged, untouched)  │
└──────────────────────────┘

Your MCP server never sees billing logic. If a caller has no credits, they get a 402 Payment Required before your server is even contacted.
